thread.title: Sun

author: Sun
title: Sun
text:
This is the second time I ordered persimmon tree from Willis.
Last year trees arrived well packed and alive but I managed to kill them by
Putting them in the wrong spots. No fault of the orchard.
This year The tree arrived well packed and beautiful looking again.
Hope I found the perfect spot for it. I am very happy with purchase.
will be coming back for more. Thank you.
Sun
